Tonya & Kyle
I’m from a small town in east-central Indiana—a true Midwestern girl! Growing up with my three sisters, my family frequently attended and participated in auctions, garage sales, flea markets, and antique shows. I loved the hustle and bustle of those events. I began my career in retail, transitioned into corporate staffing, and have spent the past 18 years in healthcare management. Along the way, I discovered that customer service and project management are my true passions. When combined with my love for all things vintage and repurposed, it led me to explore opportunities where these interests could come together. Vintage Market Days® was a natural fit—the events are a full experience the whole family can enjoy!
Once I discovered the opportunity to bring a Vintage Market Days® event to the area, I jumped at the chance—and I haven’t looked back since. I’m blessed with a supportive husband and two wonderful boys who have stood beside me every step of the way on this exciting journey into the world of Vintage Market Days®.
Can’t wait to see you there! xoxo, Tonya

Vintage Market Days® is a franchised Vintage event that began in the Tulsa area in 2011. The first VMD™ event was held in June of 2012 at Carmichael's Pumpkin Patch in Bixby, OK. By 2013, Vintage Market Days® was being "licensed" to several vendors who wanted to take Vintage Market Days® to other communities. By 2014, Vintage Market Days® had grown to 8 event locations in 5 states. It was at this point that VMD™ became a franchise business. As of January 2022, Vintage Market Days® has more than 60 franchises in 26 states across the US. We love nothing more than bringing the Vintage experience to you®. I hope you will have the opportunity to join us at one of our events this year!
- Dianna Brown

Welcome to Vintage Market Days of
Eastern Idaho
What is Vintage Market Days®?
Vintage Market Days® of Eastern Idaho is an upscale vintage-inspired, curated market featuring original art, antiques, boutique clothing, jewelry, handmade treasures, specialty items, home décor, outdoor furnishings, children’s goods, gourmet eats and treats, seasonal plantings and so much more. So much more than a flea market, our experience is a three day event held twice a year in Eastern Idaho!
Each Vintage Market Days® event is a unique opportunity for vendors to display their talents and passions in different avenues.  The market will provide the guest with a very special shopping experience with over 100 vendors to shop, featuring LIVE music and the best Eastern Idaho food and snack vendors.
Buying a cool piece of furniture at our market? We've got you! When you buy a piece of furniture you can pull right up to our loading zone and we'll load it into your car. We will also have a small item/bag check for your smaller purchases and bags in case you want to have hands-free shopping. Proceeds go to our non-profit - Idaho Foster & Adoptive Parent Association (IDFAPA) whom we LOVE working with.
Tickets may be pre-purchased here, including perks!
~Purchase our Early Buying Ticket and get first dibs on all of the one of a kind finds at our market!
~Be automatically entered to win a $200 Visa shopping spree card!
~Gain early access each day, our gate opens 30 minutes early each day for pre-purchased ticket holders!
